text: Maria Da Cruz Hernández, known as Maria Da Cruz, is an Andorran footballer who plays as a forward for Andorran-based Spanish Women's First Division of Catalonia club ENFAF and the Andorra women's national team. ==International career== Da Cruz capped for Andorra at senior level in a 1–2 friendly loss to Luxembourg in June 2019. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers Category:Andorran people of Portuguese descent Category:Andorran people of Spanish descent Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
